Hi there,
My name is Jon and I recently started my own Painting & Drywall repair company. I have 5 years of experience working for local companies In Ottawa like Valencia Painting & Drywall, Ottawa Quality Painting, and Stef's Quality Painting.

I have experience with interior, exterior, commercial, and residential jobs. My prices are affordable so please contact me for a quote

cell- 6138691057
Email- Jonathan.182000@hotmail.com
services: Interior painting Exterior Painting Drywall Repairs Commercial Painting
specialities: The application of quality finishes no matter the surface.
